Business Plan for: Nora's Cafe

Prepared by: Nora S. Ademi
Last Updated: 03.20.2011

Idea:
The idea of the Classic Cafe & Sandwich Shop is to bring a healthy life living and opportunity to enjoy the taste of fresh juice and a feel the classic style living of America. The key of communication to the classic world will be the internet into the location so the youngster will be reminded through the pictures hanged in the wall and the music which will bring atmosphere and fantastic service. 

The Business Model:
The purpose of our business is to offer healthy food and great service to costumers which will excite all ages costumers with music and hospitality.

The Customer:
Youngster will be attracted with the fresh juice plus internet, ranger will be attracted with fresh coffee, fresh bagels and  classic movie stars pictures and music that will remind their time, families with be attracted with excellent service a healthy sandwiches and homemade deserts plus have love and hospitality in the service area. 

The Competition:
Other food places are more into making the food as fast as possible and that will fulfill their needs;However our goal is  to satisfy each of the costumers with great food and service and give good time to all while they are in our place. 

The Message:
I was born  in a small country, and grow up to love America through out the movies, for instance John Wayne, Marilyn Monroe, James Dean etc,.. Thats my dream to enjoy my life in a country style life in the middle of Texas with lovable families 

The Sales Approach (edit)
Since this is an individual small business enterprise in the future we are planing to inform customers through the media, internet, and the way towards its customers. This allows the direct marketing as a specific form increasingly using communication channels that the owner has built in the past with potential customers.

The Inner Workings (edit)
Classic Cafe & Sandwich Shop will be managed by me and my husband, two cash register, three food server, and one dish washer.Part time will be server and answering the phone, in the future having a delivery guys three to five part-time position. Employs mostly will be teenagers in the morning, afternoon will be mostly by me, my wife, and other two par-time employs .It all depend how busy we will be. 

The Management Team (edit)
I will be the operator manager since i do have the experience ', and my wife will supervise the place
